{"tid":1684034,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［區選］手足完美示範玩殘建制參選人","createTime":"2019-10-31T02:11:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-12T10:55:36.000Z","uid":259980,"like":14,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"f1d40e47968d6117cd6063983a5e1160d5d75cf0","tid":1684034,"uid":259980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T02:11:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />sorry呃咗大家入嚟<br />\n其實係想講<span style=\"color: red;\">處理建制傳單</span>方法<br />\n<br />\n我覺得目前轉頭扔/當面撕都唔夠好<br />\n仲可能會營造<span style=\"color: red;\">多人攞單張受歡迎</span>嘅假象<br />\n正確方法應該係<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n攞完單張<br />\n搵個唔會有人理你亂拋垃圾嘅時機<br />\n扔係地<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">人樣朝上</span><br />\n<br />\n如果選區周地都係某個人嘅單張<br />\n比人行嚟行去踩<br />\n無人執返無人理<br />\n嗰個人嘅形象會同<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">垃圾、無用、廢物、無人想睇、不受歡迎</span><br />\n連結起嚟<br />\n<br />\n至少我家老母會：「嘩，嗰個XXX d傳單無人睇架喎，比人扔到周地都係」<br />\n<br />\n個人覺得比起當面撕/轉頭扔垃圾桶<br />\n對選情(or say<span style=\"color: red;\">社區形象</span>)更有影響力"},{"pid":"a0d420be5bd574deb85ef9fc7c87b8321cf6aad9","tid":1684034,"uid":259980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T02:11:38.000Z","msg":"補充區"},{"pid":"64324a85c862e4ad02cb87be59ddd37ccaf44868","tid":1684034,"uid":259980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T02:11:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dda94ac4b0ce04f90104a2861667da20794c66cc","tid":1684034,"uid":259980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T02:11:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dd4357ffb63549a6ec93e5b594a94e7bc57c23e5","tid":1684034,"uid":23023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T02:19:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"25c69cb6d137bbf78bbbcab62d10427db1fee14c","tid":1684034,"uid":128594,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T02:20:41.000Z","msg":"屌 成日開埋d fake topic"}